content: --अध्वन् {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {1} one who has accomplished or finished a journey; <ls>R. 4. 46</ls>, <ls n="R.">11. 33.</ls> {2} conversant, familiar (with anything). {%--<ab>f.</ab>%} the time immediately preceding new moon when a small streak of the moon is still visible; (चतुर्दशीयुक्ताऽमावास्या).
